    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/f9bc2a946873e15e99d75ba035046c45.avif?t=1737922528\" width=588 height=138 /></span></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;<strong>塔与妖精：最后的防线 演示版</strong>&quot; 是一款塔防/RTS游戏，你需要发展你的王国，管理资源，并抵御妖精的攻击。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/ad8732f5117d0e35ba098541c2a3e8cc.avif?t=1737922528\" width=586 height=134 /></span></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抵御妖精的攻击</strong>: 与各种类型的妖精战斗，保护你的王国免受摧毁。妖精如潮水般袭来，给你准备防御的时间。利用这个时间制定策略，利用王国的地理优势来强化防御。</p>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在演示版中，你将面临两场难度逐渐增加的任务，而无尽模式将在未来的更新中推出。此外，在第二个任务的结束时，还将有与“摩尔加斯征服者”的boss战斗。[ /p]<br>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/428e54bd3e9cad98d20546eead73df23.poster.avif?t=1737922528\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/428e54bd3e9cad98d20546eead73df23.webm?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/428e54bd3e9cad98d20546eead73df23.mp4?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>[/list]<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建筑和升级</strong>: 游戏中有多种建筑类型，包括基础设施、防御和资源收集。</p>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在演示版中，你可以使用特定类型的升级来提高你的塔楼。未来的更新中将添加“天赋”功能，使你能够进一步自定义塔楼的技能。</p>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/24611509c6f8e113d5b9fcde276c8f9c.poster.avif?t=1737922528\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/24611509c6f8e113d5b9fcde276c8f9c.webm?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/24611509c6f8e113d5b9fcde276c8f9c.mp4?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人口增长和管理:</strong> 招募农民和战士等单位来扩展和保护你的王国。在演示版中，只提供这两种类型的单位。</p>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/d71bf2c0c4bbcd9d1ddab3dd2e22eb26.poster.avif?t=1737922528\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/d71bf2c0c4bbcd9d1ddab3dd2e22eb26.webm?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/d71bf2c0c4bbcd9d1ddab3dd2e22eb26.mp4?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源收集和管理</strong>: 收集木材、石头和黄金等基本资源。管理你的居民，确保有足够的食物来维持他们的生活。</p>  <br>  <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/72a5647f05269d52c5175e20ab8237b6.poster.avif?t=1737922528\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/72a5647f05269d52c5175e20ab8237b6.webm?t=1737922528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285450/extras/72a5647f05